description: Stunning loft in the rarely available Court Square Press Building! 1 Bed unit that can easily be made into a 2 Bed as the developer originally intended. 2 Full Baths. HUGE, open living room and kitchen w/ dual exposures and commanding views of Back Bay and Downtown - an entertainer's dream! Exposed brick and beam with all the modern touches - granite tops, SS appliances, gas cooking, W/D in unit, Australian HW floors, central AC & heat, PLUS 1 garage parking spot! The original smoke stack was even kept intact and now functions as a luxurious walk-in shower in the master suite. Build out the second bedroom for less than $10k, add sliders for the occasional guest, or leave open and have an enormous living room that even your friends in the burbs would be jealous of! This luxury building includes 24/7 concierge, fully equipped gym, professional screening room, prep kitchen, pool and outdoor grilling on the 4th floor terrace. Steps to Whole Foods and the T!  Private showings start today.
